{
  "stem": "27340.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said they were very, very sorry, but they'd booked many, many moons before a trip to New York on the And they didn't really feel they want to cancel it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And naturally, I accepted that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had to accept whatever my seniors said to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I was there without any family at all for my bar mitzvah, which was perhaps sad, but you know, I didn't really know what bar mitzvah was all about.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Obviously, I knew the raison d'etre of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But whether this was to be a large family do or not or what, it really didn't concern me all that much.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was totally ignorant of the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I merely said the brachot when I was called up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did no reciting of a parshah or part of the sidra or the haftarah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just said the brachot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was called up and I was congratulated by everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the hostel, we had an extra piece of cake that morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were kept-- don't forget it was during the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I beg your pardon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was before the war, but the hostel, the organization ran itself on a shoestring.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And rightly so, they lavished very little luxuries on us, far from it, saving any money that they had to try and get more children out of Germany rather than let us live in some sort of luxury.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think regretfully as it was at the time-- you know, we were all used to a certain amount of luxury-- this obviously didn't play a major part in our existence.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were dressed in uniforms, as it happened to be the sort of custom in England.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
